<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_279_r1l17">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">Als </del> vns hat fürgelegt Chuncʒ flurhey <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l18">vvie 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jm </del> Er etwaʒ ſache vor <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden cʒehandeln hab von <expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan> gut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l19">wegen als Jm die 
<del rend="strikethrough">für <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> lantgeriht gen <expan>vvircʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan></del> geladen ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l20">woꝛden / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jm durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr gnade darynne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_279_r1l24">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>gutlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_279_r1l23"><expan>gnedıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab></add> beweẏſen vnd Jn 
