<add><ab facs="#facs_279_line_1576576174397_1241">gütlich </ab></add> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>hochvvirdık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
