</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_279" id="139r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Chuncz Flurhey,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie er etwaz sache vor
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden cze handeln hab von
                                <expan>sein<ex>er</ex></expan> gut wegen, als im die geladen sein
                        worden. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir im durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr gnade darynne
                                    <add><expan>gnedikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan></add> beweysen und in
                            <add>gütlich</add> von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hochwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> lassen wöllet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
